snippet.title: Rune Classic gameplay (PC Game, 2000)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Rune Classic, PC game produced by Nine Realms in 2000 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/rune-classic/16844/
Rune Classic is a nice adventure game, contain a multitude of mythical enemies, including goblins, skeletons, dwarves, snakes, Vikings, and bosses.
Played through modern Windows machine.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Thief 2: Metal Age - https://youtu.be/ZgdGB-xMaQE
Gothic - https://youtu.be/q7ZH7QDqdzE
